oses and to such extent as may be prescribed, by obligations arising under those terms and conditions (except in so far as they are inconsistent with subsection (1)), and", "enrichment_def_id" : 1, "enrichment_extent" : {"type": "xml", "sections": [{"extent_end": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/ns:mod/ns:quotedStructure/ns:chapter/ns:section[2]/ns:subsection[4]/ns:paragraph[2]", "extent_start": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/ns:mod/ns:quotedStructure/ns:chapter/ns:section[2]/ns:subsection[4]/ns:paragraph[2]", "extent_char_end": null, "extent_char_start": null}]}, "enrichment_id" : 68}, {"enrichment_value" : "The Secretary of State may make regulations specifying matters which are, or are not, to be treated as remuneration for the purposes of this section.", "enrichment_def_id" : 1, "enrichment_extent" : {"type": "xml", "sections": [{"extent_end": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/ns:mod/ns:quotedStructure/ns:chapter/ns:section[2]/ns:subsection[7]", "extent_start": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/ns:mod/ns:quotedStructure/ns:chapter/ns:section[2]/ns:subsection[7]", "extent_char_end": null, "extent_char_start": null}]}, "enrichment_id" : 69}, {"enrichment_value" : "The Secretary of State may make regulations making provision, in relation to the right to return under subsection (4)(c), about— seniority, pension rights and similar rights; terms and conditions of employment on return.", "enrichment_def_id" : 1, "enrichment_extent" : {"type": "xml", "sections": [{"extent_end": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/ns:mod/ns:quotedStructure/ns:chapter/ns:section[2]/ns:subsection[8]", "extent_start": "ns:act/ns:body/ns:part[1]/ns:chapter[1]/ns:hcontainer[1]/ns:section[3]/ns:content/ns:p[2]/n